## Data Download Commands
freqtrade download-data --userdir /allah/stuff/freq/project/user_data --config /allah/stuff/freq/project/user_data/config.json --timerange 20250501- --timeframes 1m 3m 5m 15m 30m 1h 4h --datadir /allah/freqtrade/user_data/data/binance

## Strategy Commands
freqtrade trade --strategy SimpleTestStrategy --userdir /allah/stuff/freq/project/user_data --config /allah/stuff/freq/project/user_data/config_test_5s.json 

## Backtesting Commands
freqtrade backtesting --strategy TEMAReversal_MLStrategy --userdir /allah/stuff/freq/project/user_data --config /allah/stuff/freq/project/user_data/config.json --timerange 20250701- --datadir /allah/freqtrade/user_data/data/binance --cache none --starting-balance 10000 --eps --fee 0
# --timerange 1752105600-1752109200

freqtrade backtesting --strategy TrendReversalLabelingStrategy --userdir /allah/stuff/freq/project_1/user_data --config /allah/stuff/freq/project_1/user_data/config.json --timerange 20170110- --datadir /allah/freqtrade/user_data/data/binance --cache none --starting-balance 10000000 --eps --export=signals --fee 0

